Commentary Text: Ferguson to Priyam Garg, out Bowled!! Double strike from Ferguson! Garg backed away early, showed his cards and the Kiwi is too smart to be overawed by it. Opts for the leg-cutter, no pace on it and attacks the stumps. The old-school 'you miss, I hit' stuff and Garg sees the stumps disturbed. His batting promotion to no.3 hasn't worked and he'll be disappointed with this dismissal. There was an opportunity to knock off a big score by batting up the order. Not to be. KKR are delighted and rightly so. They're back in this now through Ferguson. Priyam Garg b Ferguson 4(7)
